Rough up the lower end of a Tungsten Bead with sand paper.
<br/><br/>
Place the bead on the bill at the center of the diamond shape.
<br/><br/>
Wet the bottom of the bead with CA glue. Wait a few seconds.
<br/><br/>
Dribble thick UV resin around the edges of the bead.  Harden it with a UV light
<br/><br/>
Use a small 1/16" inch twist drill to open the hole in tie bead, all the way through the bill
